%!PS

%	This example appears in section "Using Scaling to Flip and Flop
%	the Coordinate System" in Chapter 4 - "Transformations".
%
%	Caveats:	Requires PostScript Level 2.

/inch { 72 mul } def		%  define inch procedure
/Arial findfont		%  find Sonata font
6 inch scalefont		%  make large size
setfont				%  make current font
2.5 inch 2.625 inch moveto	%  set current point
/A glyphshow		%  image character by name
showpage			%  display page
